00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:21,400
(Every era has its own rules.)

342
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:25,110
(Although I can travel
to any point in time,)

343
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:27,830
(once the rules are broken repeatedly,)

344
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:30,720
(disturbances to time
and space will occur.)

345
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:39,720
(I returned to that great fire
countless times.)

346
00:27:40,310 --> 00:27:42,270
(Not only could I change nothing,)

347
00:27:42,590 --> 00:27:45,440
