434
00:32:37,590 --> 00:32:39,200
Memory loss, or something else?

435
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,040
I didn't.

436
00:32:41,666 --> 00:32:43,270
There's nothing wrong with your turtle.

437
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:44,666
Not eating is probably

438
00:32:44,666 --> 00:32:46,911
a stress response caused
by a change in the environment.

439
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,510
I'll have Dr. Tang

440
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:50,244
prescribe some vitamins for your turtle.

441
00:32:50,311 --> 00:32:51,800
It should improve after taking them.

442
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:53,400
You can wait outside now.

443
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:04,140
(Haidong Province, Ninghai)

444
00:33:04,910 --> 00:33:05,760
What are you doing?

445
00:33:05,790 --> 00:33:07,400
This place has all sorts of people.

446
00:33:07,750 --> 00:33:09,480
You don't wish to draw attention.

447
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:10,400
I get it.

448
00:33:12,350 --> 00:33:13,640
This is my address.

449
00:33:13,830 --> 00:33:15,960
When you feel the timing is right,

450
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:17,200
come and find me anytime.

451
00:33:17,510 --> 00:33:18,920
I'll take Xuan Wu and go first.

452
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:27,480
These past ten years,

453
00:33:28,310 --> 00:33:30,160
I've always kept our friendship in mind.

454
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:32,550
That you're still alive

455
00:33:32,830 --> 00:33:34,270
is already the greatest miracle.

456
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:37,480
I won't ask for anything more.

457
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:50,030
What a pity.

458
00:33:50,750 --> 00:33:52,440
In the prime of his life,

459
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:54,780
yet mentally unbalanced.

460
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:58,460
(Yashe)

461
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:04,840
Sorry.

462
00:34:05,590 --> 00:34:06,960
I only bought you back on a whim

463
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:08,710
because I needed to see my friend.

464
00:34:09,070 --> 00:34:10,360
But you have to believe me.

465
00:34:10,688 --> 00:34:12,550
I'm not someone
who abandons things halfway.

466
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,360
I'll treat you well.

467
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:27,880
(Fish-patterned Mirror
expires on March 16.)

468
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:29,230
(Time is limited.)

469
00:34:29,288 --> 00:34:31,190
(It's best to retrieve it
as soon as possible.)

470
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:40,400
Yashe?

471
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:41,630
Quite a distinctive name.

472
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:43,920
You did come after all.

473
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,480
Of course, I did.

474
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:47,190
You forgot your medicine.

475
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:51,070
Thank you.

476
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,840
Do you know how to
give medicine to a turtle?

477
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:53,760
Want some help?

478
00:34:54,110 --> 00:34:54,950
That'd be great.

479
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,240
Please, come in.

480
00:34:58,300 --> 00:35:01,420
(Yashe)

481
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,360
Where's Xuan Wu?

482
00:35:03,510 --> 00:35:04,760
You finally remember me.

483
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:06,070
Are you thinking of going back?

484
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:08,000
No. Where's Xuan Wu?

485
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:09,490
That's not important. It's over there.

486
00:35:09,550 --> 00:35:10,390
I can immediately...

487
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:11,400
Xuan Wu.

488
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,030
I brought you medicine.

489
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:17,590
It's not there either.

490
00:35:17,590 --> 00:35:18,520
Forget about Xuan Wu.

491
00:35:18,530 --> 00:35:19,800
It's gone where it belongs.

492
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:21,320
You need to go back where you belong.

493
00:35:22,510 --> 00:35:23,880
I'll send you back right now.

494
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:27,000
Okay. Let me tell you
how to give the turtle its medicine.

495
00:35:27,550 --> 00:35:29,030
First is medicine number one.

496
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:31,030
Find a bowl about this big,

497
00:35:31,030 --> 00:35:33,670
