502
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,000
to dissolve it into a liquid.

503
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,280
See if it'll drink it.

504
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:44,800
If it still won't drink,

505
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:46,880
then you'll need
a thinner pair of chopsticks,

506
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,070
about this thin.

507
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:53,710
(So he really was just here
to deliver the medicine.)

508
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:58,350
Are you listening?

509
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:00,440
You don't remember anything,

510
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:02,390
