511
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,200
I...

512
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:06,110
I remember.

513
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:07,920
We were both drunk last night.

514
00:36:08,110 --> 00:36:09,550
I walked you to your doorstep.

515
00:36:09,550 --> 00:36:11,360
I said I wouldn't come in,
but you insisted.

516
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:14,910
Then, I helped you over to this sofa.

517
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,630
When I opened my eyes again,
